{"type": "article", "id": 21474, "title": "啤酒包装", "description": "", "date": "2016-01-29T07:34:02Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 33, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606071042003m4N5MBaAKfZcnos.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是一款产于巴西的啤酒，最明显的标志是它的手写字体 SaLVA，占据了大部分篇幅。标签的背后采用黄、粉、绿、蓝等亮丽的颜色，吸引人们寻找不同颜色包装的兴趣。瓶口处的颜色与瓶身上一致，有简洁时尚的海报感。这款啤酒的包装并不复杂，但通过夸张的文字可以看到啤酒本身洋溢的年轻的热情。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726151005z4icCUbVDQ78nagR.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"708\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.65555556\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726151005iCHzsDjYKQtu0UPO.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"540\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261510064lK8jEV9MtzbZ1CP.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"717\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726151007EpZCTwxVSlM2jtmH.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"1626\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.50555556\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}